      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      211.61,
      261.05,
      565.03,
      273.05
    ],
    "text": "obtain the title deed, if any, of such property, and make an",
