      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      67.58,
      534.79,
      564.93,
      546.79
    ],
    "text": "entire case. Appellant\u2019s pedigree is silent on deed 13486 and according to the entry made by N.P. on",
